    "spell_type": "spell",
    "subtype": "spell",
    "text": "You conjure a temporary simple tool, such as a shovel or rope into your hands. It lasts until it\u2019s used for a single activity or for 1 minute, whichever comes first, after which it disappears. The tool is obviously temporarily conjured and thus can\u2019t be sold or passed off as a genuine item.",
